<section class="sec" style="background:var(--w)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-hd reveal">
      <span class="tag">What You Get</span>
      <h2 class="hdg">Everything Included in <span class="b">Your Evaluation</span></h2>
      <div class="div div-c"></div>
      <p class="sub">One powerful session designed to give you real answers and a clear path forward.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2col reveal" style="gap:16px">
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128270;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Behavior Root Cause Analysis</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Jas digs deep to find WHY your dog behaves the way it does &mdash; not just what it does.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128203;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Custom Action Plan</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">You leave with a specific, written roadmap tailored to your dog's personality and your lifestyle.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#127775;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">One-on-One with Jas</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">This is not an assistant or junior trainer. You get Jas Leverette directly.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128218;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Handler Education</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Learn the principles that make training stick &mdash; understanding that travels with you everywhere.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#127919;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Training Priority Roadmap</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Know exactly what to work on first, second, and third for the fastest transformation.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128241;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Program Recommendation</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">If your dog needs more work, Jas recommends the exact right next step &mdash; no upsell pressure.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128276;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Real-World Context Assessment</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">We assess your dog in the environment where problems actually happen.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#9989;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Honest Answers</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">No fluff, no filler. Just straight talk about what your dog needs and how to get there.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Eval What's Included",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Eval What's Included" }]
}
{% endschema %}
